A minimalistic composition featuring a single elegant ceramic cup of dark coffee viewed from above, with the liquid's surface showing subtle swirling patterns that form an intricate, organic code-like structure. The cup sits on a pristine white surface with a single perfect origami crane casting a delicate shadow nearby. The scene is rendered in muted earth tones—warm browns, soft grays, and cream—with dramatic natural lighting from one side creating refined contrast. The aesthetic suggests discernment, refinement, and the careful appreciation of craft over quantity.
